# 🏥 NHS Capacity and Resource Utilisation Analysis

## 📋 Overview
This project was completed as part of the **Data Analytics Career Accelerator** from **TheLondon School of Economics and Political Science (LSE)** in collaboration with FourthRev.

**Objective:**  
To help the **National Health Service (NHS)** assess whether to expand its capacity by analyzing utilisation trends across its healthcare networks.

---

## 🎯 Business Problem
> “NHS needs to budget correctly when expanding its infrastructure and resources to match its increasing population capacity.”

Key analytical questions:
1. What was the actual utilisation of NHS resources?  
2. Has there been adequate staff and capacity across networks?  
3. Should NHS increase its capacity?

